results.name: Decimal expansion of m = (1-1/e^2)/2, one of Renyi's parking constants.
comment: Curiously, this Renyi parking constant is very close to the prime generated continued fraction A084255 (gap ~ 10^-7).
reference: Steven R. Finch, Mathematical Constants, Cambridge University Press, 2003, Section 5.3 Renyi's parking constant, p. 280.
link: Marek Wolf, Continued fractions constructed from prime numbers, arxiv.org/abs/1003.4015, pp. 4-5.
results.author: _Jean-François Alcover_, Sep 25 2014
